Arsenal Defender Andre Santos to Miss Three Months After Surgery on Ankle

-- B y   C h r i s t o p h e r   E l s e r
-- 
2011-12-12T15:32:08Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-12/arsenal-defender-andre-santos-to-miss-three-months-after-surgery-on-ankle.html
Arsenal defender Andre Santos will
miss three months after undergoing surgery this week on his
injured ankle, the English Premier League soccer club said.  The left back will have an operation this week in  Brazil  to
repair ligament damage in his right foot, the London team said
today in a statement on its website. He was hurt in a Champions
League match against Olympiacos last week.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Christopher Elser at 
 celser@bloomberg.net  